title: HyPrSpace looks for applications beyond launch for its hybrid propulsion technology
description:
A French launch startup that recently closed a funding round is seeking defense applications for its hybrid propulsion technology.

The post HyPrSpace looks for applications beyond launch for its hybrid propulsion technology appeared first on SpaceNews.
